Show version and exit.
.TP
.B \\-\\-usage
Show usage information and exit.
.TP
.B \\-\\-install
Install shell completions and initialize config.
.TP
.B \\-\\-uninstall
Uninstall shell completions and cleanup.
.TP
.B \\-\\-quiet, \\-q
Suppress all log output.
.TP
.B \\-\\-verbose, \\-v
Enable verbose logging.
